 1997-04291997-03-210,  AGRI-FOOD,  ,  , 
PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-68 of January 7, 1997 which will extend the appointment of BARRY SENFT as a commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission until March 31, 2002; and designation of BARRY SENFT, of Regina, Saskatchewan, as chief commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission to hold office during pleasure, effective April 1, 1997.
